== Sources ==
[../include/images/Source-code-icon.png]

- The sources of this web site, captions and subtitles can be found [here https://github.com/vitalyrepin/FreedomRMS/].  Feel free to re-use them for your own projects with respect
to the [Creative Commons licenses ../license/index.html] these materials are distributed under.
- Video files are located in the ['rms' subfolder of this site http://vrepin.org/rms/] and can be easily fetched with [wget https://www.gnu.org/software/wget/].


== Tools ==
[../include/images/crafty-penguin.png]

The following free tools were used in order to prepare this course:

- [Txt2Site Website Builder  http://home.deds.nl/~svg_experimenten/txt2site/] to build this web site
- [txt2tags http://txt2tags.org/], [LaTeX http://www.latex-project.org/], [LibreOffice Impress https://www.libreoffice.org/discover/impress/] and [Gimp http://www.gimp.org/] to create documents and slides
- [PGF/TikZ http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PGF/TikZ] to draw nice [mindmap http://vrepin.org/rms/W1/FourFreedomsPatents.pdf]
- [ffmpeg https://www.ffmpeg.org/] and [Kdenlive https://kdenlive.org/] for video postprocessing
- [Subtitleeditor http://home.gna.org/subtitleeditor/] to create subtitles
- [GNU Make https://www.gnu.org/software/make/] to put it all together
- [Vim http://www.vim.org/about.php] was used as an editor ( sorry, rms! [Emacs http://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/] is great editor too, everybody knows  :-) )

